text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea carapae is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family. It is found in Peninsular Malaysia and Borneo.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea carapae". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T31915A9667865. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31915A9667865.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
